pullRequest.body:
The PR generalizes universes for `standardSimplex`, which is now a functor `SimplexCategory ⥤ SSet.{u}` for any universe `u`.

---

@jcommelin : we can wait you have finished showing that nerves of categories are quasi-categories before proceeding with this PR.
